[43.316831, "o", "\u001b[32;1mdone.\u001b[0;22m\r\n\r\n\u001b[32;1m  ✓ Commit successful!\u001b[0;22m\r\n\r\n  Git commit:  d27500a\r\n  Message:     protecting my code\r\n  Files:       21\r\n  Root hash:   105d7cd6b68949f317ba01dcaabda400...\r\n  Timestamp:   2026-03-19T20:31:42Z\r\n\u001b[36m  Mode:        proof-only (no encryption — code is readable)\r\n\u001b[0m\r\n  Run 'sentinel push'         to push to remote.\r\n  Run 'sentinel proof status' to check Bitcoin confirmation.\r\n\r\n"]
